ase visit https://www.newsfilecorp.com/release/204134  SOURCE: Social Impact Partners\", \"from\": 4394, \"to\": 4631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4409, \"end\": 4415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edmund_Bonner\", \"score\": 0.9981575907376701, \"rank\": 0.0018458053222010341, \"text\": \"Bonner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edmund_Bonner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edmund_Bonner\"}, {\"begin\": 4616, \"end\": 4631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Impact_Partners\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Impact Partners\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Impact_Partners\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Impact_Partners\"}]}]}"